  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK913">
<l>poruṭpeṇṭir poymmai muyakka miruṭṭaṟaiyil</l>
<l>ētil piṇantaḻīi yaṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The false embraces of wealth-loving women are like (hired men) embracing a strange corpse in a dark room.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
